    "name": "Cosmo's Industry",
    "steam_appid": 3330510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/2119b19ad25b2fa4a1acd2c7e36c01ad.avif?t=1764849867\" width=1560 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Cosmo's industry</u> is all about capitalism, that's why you either adapt or join the other's under the overpass huddled next to a trashcan fire. <br><br><br>You as a new business owner, or I guess old business owner have the task of not only surviving the vast emptiness of space, but also satisfy your customers no mater what weird and disgusting thing they may need. So be ready to work you ass off until you achieve wealth or die trying.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock and See</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 Rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ Items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ Customers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ Skills and upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Minigames</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/bb4855c8d52aad4545dfd337bd97b4c2.poster.avif?t=1764849867\" width=1170 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/bb4855c8d52aad4545dfd337bd97b4c2.webm?t=1764849867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/bb4855c8d52aad4545dfd337bd97b4c2.mp4?t=1764849867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upkeep Your Shop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy and sell to anyone you see. Making money is your most important goal and you do that through the shop window. You can buy materials easily and make whatever you need or want. Selling complicated items nets you some good profit, but selling under the right conditions can give you a even BIGGER bag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/5d938db5cbc7a5e61523c5dfc95a510a.poster.avif?t=1764849867\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/5d938db5cbc7a5e61523c5dfc95a510a.webm?t=1764849867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/5d938db5cbc7a5e61523c5dfc95a510a.mp4?t=1764849867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite space being a lonely place you wont be alone and the only company you'll have is not only the customers you may come across but also your business partner/employee/the responsible one/maintenance guy. He may seem friendly but don't piss him off because he is the only reason your shop is still standing (even though the state its in isn't all that impressive).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong></strong><br><br><strong>Collect and Craft</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All items need to be crafted out of items that also need to be crafted... You do that by completing minigames once you start the crafting process. As a businessman, you want to cut costs and increase profit, and so you need to do everything yourself. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/079917c756b099205e079374c8b95b59.poster.avif?t=1764849867\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/079917c756b099205e079374c8b95b59.webm?t=1764849867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/079917c756b099205e079374c8b95b59.mp4?t=1764849867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Any questions? No problem - Join the discord and leave any feedback or opinions.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330510/extras/94b1f90f0a2ccb6a7110468bf7dc2803.avif?t=1764849867\" width=1560 height=122 /></span></p>",
